text: pitabrakd nasa nowknong( kar dak tearounakamm)noh kuchea phosdo tang muoy samreab anak del ban khlach tearounakamm nea thngai barlok . now thngai noh mnoussa lok trauv ban ke bramoulophdom samreab trong . haey now thngai noh der avei teangoasa ku nung trauv mean v tdama n ( daembi katsechakdei)
